replies.body:
I'm truly sorry you had to experience that.  Unfortunately in this life people for no reason get seriously angry if they are having a bad game. 
Like me. Do I get angry? Hell yeah, when im getting hammered into the ground.  Do I call people horrible names? Yes, but starting today I am dismantling all chat, in hopes of finding peace and fun, instead of other toxic people.  New Season. New Habits.  ALL FOR ONE, ONE FOR ALL... LIFE, LIBERTY, AND PURSUIT OF HAPPINESS!!! 
